OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783792086
OL,3,CLongest-serving Archers actor Patricia
OL,4,CGreene dies aged 95
OL,6,FPatricia Greene, the longest
OL,7,Fcontinuously serving actor in the
OL,8,Fsoap, The Archers, has died aged 95.
OL,10,FThe star, who was born in Derby,
OL,11,Fplayed Jill Archer, a mother who was
OL,12,Fknown for her lemon drizzle cake, in
OL,13,Fthe long-running radio show from 1957
OL,14,Funtil her death.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
