OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1783792086
OL,3,CLongest-serving Archers actor Patricia
OL,4,CGreene dies aged 95
OL,6,FThe Archers has aired on BBC radio
OL,7,Fsince 1951 and has clocked up more
OL,8,Fthan 20,000 episodes ` more than any
OL,9,Fother continuous drama serial in the
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,FIt reaches millions of devoted fans
OL,13,Fwho tune in to hear the ups and downs
OL,14,Fexperienced by the residents of the
OL,15,Ffictional village of Ambridge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
