OL,4,CGreene dies aged 95
OL,6,FPressing topical issues such as
OL,7,Fclimate change, the economic
OL,8,Fchallenges faced by farmers,
OL,9,Falcoholism, modern slavery, domestic
OL,10,Fabuse and coercive control have all
OL,11,Fbeen tackled by the show.
